<h2>Grooved tongue, Sore tongue and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms grooved tongue, sore tongue and white patches on tongue including Fissured tongue, Medication reaction or side-effect, and Allergic reaction.</p>
